Subject: Stale content
Description: Is there a means to define the Stale parameter for the File System module to not just one year but possibly to 8, 9 or 10 years? Or can a report be configure to pull data based on a modified stale date parameter?
What_We_Know__c: The customer needs to manipulate the Stale Content data to display more than one year of Stale data.
Solution_Comment__c: I helped the customer modify the SQL script for the SA_ENG_FSAA_FolderAging.
